how to show text on heat map or any thing acording to value zero or one: (in value of parameter is 0 then it will show 1st statment, if value is 1 it will show 2nd statment)

1st define Parameters:
than use this DAX:

HeatMap Caption = 
    VAR _SelectedMeasure = 
    SELECTEDVALUE(Parameter[Parameter Order])
    RETURN
    IF( _SelectedMeasure = 0,
       "Darkest Purple color shows maximum satisfaction",
       "Darkest Red color shows maximum wait time")
